Convert the given buisness problem to a mathematical problem

eg:-If I want to increase the revenue of Netflix then one option I have is to increase the number of customers,second option is to charge high and the last option is to decrease the churn rate.
    So I prefer the third one.So My buisness problem has been reduced to decrease the churn rate from 4 percent to 3.75percent
    
    churn rate:-Number of customers leaving netflix
